MoonSharp.​Interpreter.​DataStructs.​LinkedListIndex
internal
MoonSharp.​Interpreter.​DataStructs.​LinkedListIndex​<TKey, TValue>

An index to accelerate operations on a LinkedListTValue using a single key of type TKey More than one LinkedListIndex can index the same linked list, but every node in the linked list must be indexed by one and only one LinkedListIndex object.

Type Parameters
TKey

The type of the key. Must implement Equals and GetHashCode appropriately.

TValue

The type of the values contained in the linked list.
